VIRTUAL HAUNTED HOUSE WITH PYTHON AND TKINTER

DESCRIPTION: DEVELOP A GRAPHICAL
INTERFACE WITH TKINTER THAT
SIMULATES A HAUNTED HOUSE. THE
APPLICATION SHOULD ALLOW THE
USER TO INTERACT WITH OBJECTS IN
THE HOUSE, SUCH AS TURNING ON
LIGHTS, ACTIVATING CREEPY
SOUNDS, AND OPENING OR CLOSING
VIRTUAL DOORS.

OBJECTIVE: USE TKINTER TO CREATE
THE GRAPHICAL INTERFACE AND
HANDLE EVENTS LIKE BUTTON CLICKS,
AS WELL AS INTEGRATE SOUNDS
WITH PYGAME OR PLAYSOUND.

DIFFICULTY: MEDIUM-HIGH


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Make sure to: 
pip install playsound
pip install pillow